#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:1
msgid "Pioneer DDJ-SX"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:4
msgid ""
"The Pioneer DDJ-SX is a 4 deck all-in-one controller that provides intuitive"
" control of all of Mixxx’s features. The DDJ-SX mapping [reportedly works "
"with the DDJ-SX2](https://mixxx.discourse.group/t/pioneer-ddj-sx-controller-"
"mapping/15954/22), but it does not use the new features of the DDJ-SX2 "
"hardware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:7
msgid ""
"[Manufacturer’s product "
"page](https://www.pioneerdj.com/en/product/controller/archive/ddj-"
"sx/black/overview/)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:8
msgid ""
"[Forum thread](https://mixxx.discourse.group/t/pioneer-ddj-sx-controller-"
"mapping/15954)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:9
msgid ""
"[User Manual](https://support.pioneerdj.com/hc/en-"
"us/articles/22976453073305-How-to-use-the-Pioneer-DJ-DDJ-SX-DJ-Controller-"
"Instruction-manual)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:13
msgid "User Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:16
msgid ""
"To change the mapping’s user options, you have to open the script file "
"(*.js). At the top of the file under **USER OPTIONS** the following settings"
" can be made:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:18
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.jogwheelSensivity**: Sets the jogwheel sensitivity. 1 = "
"default, 2 is twice as sensitive, 0.5 is half as sensitive."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:19
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.jogwheelShiftMultiplier**: Sets how much more sensitive the "
"jogwheels get when holding {hwlabel}`SHIFT`. Set it to 1 to disable jogwheel"
" sensitivity increase when holding {hwlabel}`SHIFT`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:20
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.twinkleVumeterAutodjOn**: If true, level-meter twinkles if "
"*AutoDJ* is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:21
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.autoDJAddTop**: If true, the selected track will be added to "
"*AutoDJ* queue-top on pressing {hwlabel}`ROTARY SELECTOR`, else the selected"
" track will be added to *AutoDJ* queue-bottom."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:22
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.autoDJTickInterval**: Sets the duration of sleeping between "
"*AutoDJ* actions if *AutoDJ* is enabled [ms]."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:23
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.autoDJMaxBpmAdjustment**: Sets the maximum adjustment of BPM "
"allowed for beats to sync if *AutoDJ* is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:24
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.autoDJShuffleAfterSkip**: If true, *AutoDJ* queue is being "
"shuffled after skipping a track."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:25
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.jumpPreviewEnabled**: If true, by releasing the Rotary "
"Selector, track in preview player jumps forward to ``jumpPreviewPosition``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:26
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.jumpPreviewPosition**: Sets the preview player absolute "
"position, being set at releasing Rotary Selector and if "
"``jumpPreviewEnabled`` enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:27
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.samplerCueGotoAndPlay**: If true, pad press in "
"{hwlabel}`SAMPLER PAD MODE` repeatedly causes *sampler* to play loaded track"
" from cue-point, else it causes to play loaded track from the beginning."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:29
msgid ""
"**PioneerDDJSX.autoPFL**: If true, PFL / Cue (headphone) is being activated "
"by loading a track into certain deck."
msgstr ""

