#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:230
msgid "Continuous slice mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:233
msgid ""
"The pad lights show the active part in the active section: The active part "
"pad is lit, all other pad lights are off."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:235
msgid ""
"Continuous slice mode moves to the next section if the end of the previous "
"active section is reached."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:237
#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:243
msgid "Pioneer DDJ SX Slicer (type 1)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:245
msgid ""
"By pressing pad X, the play position jumps to the beat X of the active "
"section. If you have pressed the pad on-beat and hold it, the play position "
"is playing in loop. The beat loop length depends on the selected slicer "
"quantization (changeable by pressing {hwlabel}`PARAMETER LEFT` or "
"{hwlabel}`PARAMETER RIGHT`). If you release the pad, the playback will "
"resume where the track would have been if the slicer wouldn’t have been "
"activated (slip mode)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:249
msgid "Loop slice mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:252
msgid ""
"The pad lights show the active part in the active section: The active part "
"pad light is off, all other pads are lit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:254
msgid ""
"As soon as loop slice mode is activated, the active section is played in "
"loop (not visible in waveform). If the end of the active section is reached,"
" the play position jumps back to the beginning of the active section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:257
#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:264
msgid "Pioneer DDJ SX Slicer (type 2)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:266
msgid ""
"By pressing pad X, the play position jumps to the beat X of the active "
"section. In loop slice mode beat loop is not possible."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:268
msgid ""
"As soon as loop slice mode is deactivated (by pressing {hwlabel}`SLICER` "
"mode button again), the playback will resume where the track would have been"
" if the slicer wouldn’t have been activated (slip mode)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:273
msgid "SAMPLER Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:261
msgid ""
"Sample deck index 1 (according sampler bank) - empty: Load selected track "
"into sample deck, track loaded: start play (default, see user options) "
"sample deck"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:261
msgid ""
"Sample deck index 1 (according sampler bank) - playing: stop deck, stopped: "
"eject track"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:261
msgid ""
"Sample deck index 2 (according sampler bank) - empty: Load selected track "
"into sample deck, track loaded: start play (default, see user options) "
"sample deck"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:261
msgid ""
"Sample deck index 2 (according sampler bank) - playing: stop deck, stopped: "
