#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:368
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Solução de Problemas"

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:371
msgid ""
"If you experience any strange behavior of a button or a LED (e.g. wheel LEDs"
" not working), make sure your controller is set up correctly to work with "
"Mixxx. The DDJ-SX provides several settings, which can be changed in a "
"special *Utility-Mode*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:374
msgid "Utility-Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:377
msgid "Disconnect USB-cable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:378
msgid "Switch off {hwlabel}`STANDBY/ON` the unit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:379
msgid ""
"Hold {hwlabel}`SHIFT` button and {hwlabel}`PLAY/PAUSE` button at the left "
"deck while switching on the unit {hwlabel}`STANDBY/ON`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:380
msgid "Now *Utility-Mode* is activated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:381
msgid ""
"For saving and exiting *Utility-Mode*, switch off the unit again "
"{hwlabel}`STANDBY/ON`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:383
msgid "Setting for usage of Serato DJ"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:386
msgid ""
"To use the DDJ-SX with Mixxx, the controller must be configured for the "
"usage of Serato DJ. You can check/change this setting by pressing the "
"{hwlabel}`KEY LOCK` button at the left deck."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:388
msgid ""
"{hwlabel}`KEY LOCK` button off: Controller is configured for using Serato DJ"
" (default)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sx.md:389
msgid ""
"{hwlabel}`KEY LOCK` button on (lit): Controller is configured for using "
"different DJ-software."
msgstr ""
